    {
      "label": "check_exponent_optimality",
      "instructions": "Verify if the exponent beta = 4/3 is the critical threshold for the De Giorgi-type recurrence relation in the context of 3D Navier-Stokes equations. Determine if any beta < 4/3 violates the energy inequality or the scaling properties of the equation."
